snippet.title: Strafe Trailer
snippet.description:
This ridiculous 90s-style trailer for the Kickstarter game, Strafe, is the best thing we've seen in a while.

Check out the Kickstarter page here:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/strafegame/strafe
